<h2 id="34-use-case-modelling">3.4 Use Case Modelling</h2>
<h3 id="341-actors">3.4.1 Actors</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Educator (Admin):</strong> A registered user with instructor-level privileges; creates and manages quizzes; views class results.</li>
<li><strong>Student:</strong> A registered user with learner-level privileges; takes quizzes; views personal results.</li>
<li><strong>Gemini AI:</strong> External AI service that receives question-answer pairs and returns grading results.</li>
<li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Backend-as-a-service providing database, authentication, and storage.</li>
</ul>
